title: The YouTuber Who Thinks Australia Doesn't Exist

media:group.media:title: The YouTuber Who Thinks Australia Doesn't Exist
media:group.media:description:
Out of every conspiracy theory thought up by mankind, "Australia Doesn't Exist" has to be the nuttiest. So nutty, you might expect nobody in the world to believe it. However, YouTuber RagReynolds is one of the few who is pushing this conspiracy theory into the mainstream. It makes flat earth seem like a logical theory, and it makes for some great entertainment.

This is, The YouTuber Who Thinks Australia Doesn't Exist.
